  "keyFeatures": [
    "Cross-platform graphics API supporting Vulkan, Metal, D3D12, OpenGL, WebGL2, and WebGPU",
    "Safe, pure-Rust implementation with no unsafe code at the user level",
    "WebGPU-based API design, serving as the backend for Firefox, Servo, and Deno",
    "Naga shader translator supporting WGSL, SPIR-V, and GLSL input",
    "WebAssembly support for running in browsers via WebGPU or WebGL2",
    "Experimental ray tracing and mesh shader extensions",
    "Comprehensive validation and error reporting through wgpu-core",
    "no_std support with optional parking_lot for embedded/constrained environments"
  ],
